    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019ve absolutely loved every minute with this beauty, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home where she'll be just as cherished. Honestly, she\u2019s been pampered like a member of the family\u2014always tucked away in the garage and hand-washed every single weekend. It\u2019s rare to find one in such breathtaking shape; the paint still has that deep, mirror-like shine and the interior feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. There might be a tiny, microscopic mark on the rim if you really go looking for it, but she\u2019s truly a dream come true for any enthusiast. I\u2019m looking for a fellow car lover who will appreciate her as much as I have!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
