      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a mechanically superior E46 M3, a specimen that has been fastidiously maintained for the discerning purist. The S54 inline-six remains the pinnacle of atmospheric induction, demonstrating exceptional compression across all banks with zero oil consumption. This chassis has been fully sorted: the rear subframe has been reinforced with structural plates to mitigate any fatigue, and the VANOS system was completely overhauled using Beisan seals and a cryo-treated hub for absolute reliability. I\u2019ve optimized the suspension kinematics with a set of adjustable dampers tuned for high-speed stability and minimal body roll, while the braking system features upgraded stainless lines for a firm, communicative pedal feel. Every bushing has been replaced with high-durometer components to eliminate deflection under lateral load. This is a turn-key platform delivering a visceral, analog experience that modern cars simply cannot replicate.",
      "price": 48950.0,
